paragraphs.item: I am currently a Marketing Data Opeartions Analyst at Keysight Technologies, where I began working in May of 2022. Before that, I spent 2.5 years at UnitedHealth Group, completing Optum's Consulting Development Program and joining United HealthCare's Pharmacy Trend Analytics team, as the West Region Lead.

Before my professional career began, I studied at the University of St. Thomas and graduated Summa Cum Laude in May 2019 with degrees in Computer Science (B.A.) as well as Supply Chain & Operations Management (B.A.), and a minor in Data Analytics. At St. Thomas I played rugby for all 4 years. In my time, I served as match secretary for 1 semester, and as captain for 1 year.

In my free time, I enjoy watching sports of all kinds, I am a fan of the Milwaukee Brewers and Bucks, Wisconsin Badgers, Minnesota Vikings and Wild, Arsenal FC, Saracens RFC. I have recently begun coaching youth basketball for Minneapolis Parks & Rec.
